An **Account** is a business. Use it to group marketing campaigns and ads.

If you're a marketing agency, each Account should be one of your clients.
That way you can create separate campaigns for each one of them.

If you're not an agency and is only using our API for you own business, then you
should likely have only one Account.

Remember to link your account to external services with the `service_configurations` attribute.

